“This song fits the theme of the album because it’s me thinking about the life I have now and the blessings that are in it while also reminiscing about what I had to overcome to get here,” Rod Wave tells Apple Music. The Florida rapper/singer headlines today’s New Music Daily with “Crazy,” a track off his just-released album Nostalgia which also features an interpolation of the chorus from Paramore’s “Ain’t It Fun.” “The Paramore line brings it all together because the song is about what the ‘real world’ has been like for me and growing and maturing.” Have a listen and add this playlist to your library to stay up on the latest must-hear new songs.
